{"tid":741977,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"喜歡異世界穿越作品的多是大叔？網友：逃避現實","createTime":"2018-07-14T07:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T10:58:04.000Z","uid":49391,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ab65c7294721b51779e442bfd7ba4b92548ea0f8","tid":741977,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:16:04.000Z","msg":"幾乎每一季度的新番動畫都會出現異世界穿越題材的作品，而推崇這些作品的人居然多是三四十歲的大叔？這個結論被刊登在報紙上後，網友們對此展開討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180714_sy_225_3/gamersky_01small_02_20187149568EB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180714_sy_225_3%2Fgamersky_01small_02_20187149568EB.jpg&h=5e439407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年6月，日本經濟新聞報紙刊登了一篇報導，內容分析異世界作品的主要粉絲是30到40歲的大叔，原因是他們都由於人生不如意而夢想著能夠&ldquo;重來一次&rdquo;，並且穿越之後可以實現各種遙不可及的願望。然而從報紙發行之後到現在的一個多月時間裡，許多日本網友依然對此爭論不休，有人認為這種作品更受未成年人喜愛，也有人覺得報紙說得沒錯，逃避現實是必須的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180714_sy_225_3/gamersky_03small_06_20187149562AC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180714_sy_225_3%2Fgamersky_03small_06_20187149562AC.jpg&h=fc47004c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本經濟新聞的這篇報導指出異世界和穿越類輕小說靠著30到40歲的大叔的廣泛支持而超越了傳統的校園題材，因為許多劇中主角都是在現實失意，卻在異世界大顯身手闖出一片天，非常符合大叔們想要人生&ldquo;重來一次&rdquo;的願望。比如上個季度播出的《爆肝工程師的異世界狂想曲》裡，男主角原本是一名整天忙於工作的社畜，穿越到異世界後瞬間就成了超強冒險者，並且受到各種美少女的追捧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180714_sy_225_3/gamersky_04small_08_2018714956A6D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180714_sy_225_3%2Fgamersky_04small_08_2018714956A6D.jpg&h=01ae4c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然原作者們並未指出這種作品更加適合哪個年齡層的讀者，但不少日本網友卻為了這篇報導爭論了一個多月時間，很多人都覺得既然是動漫題材，那麼這種異世界作品應該比較受未成年人歡迎才對，主要的粉絲怎麼可能是大叔呢？不過也有人覺得大叔的確需要逃避現實的渠道，閱讀這種爽快的內容更能讓人放鬆。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180714_sy_225_3/gamersky_06small_12_20187149566DB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180714_sy_225_3%2Fgamersky_06small_12_20187149566DB.jpg&h=79a0f31b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;人生失敗組真的會想要去異世界開無雙嗎？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180714_sy_225_3/gamersky_07small_14_2018714956563.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180714_sy_225_3%2Fgamersky_07small_14_2018714956563.jpg&h=62a98bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;應該有阿宅管理層人士會想要逃避現實吧&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180714_sy_225_3/gamersky_08small_16_2018714956BEB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180714_sy_225_3%2Fgamersky_08small_16_2018714956BEB.jpg&h=7cec058b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;可以理解有人只寫得出這種作品，但卻很難理解只讀這種作品的人&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180714_sy_225_3/gamersky_09small_18_20187149563A4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180714_sy_225_3%2Fgamersky_09small_18_20187149563A4.jpg&h=a566bdbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;這種人就是碰過很多挫折卻無法跨越吧？最後只能看這種逃避現實的作品&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180714_sy_225_3/gamersky_10small_20_2018714956ABF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180714_sy_225_3%2Fgamersky_10small_20_2018714956ABF.jpg&h=457548d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;人們不都是喜歡三國誌或幕末志士那種英雄故事嗎？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180714_sy_225_3/gamersky_11small_22_201871495614F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180714_sy_225_3%2Fgamersky_11small_22_201871495614F.jpg&h=22b55d99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;大叔才不會喜歡看男主角從失敗中成長的故事啦&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　從客觀條件考慮，如果倒退十幾年的話這些所謂的&ldquo;大叔&rdquo;也是追新番看輕小說的年輕人，這樣一來年齡跨度就顯得比較合理了。再加上平時工作的壓力，誠如網友所言，這些被工作支配生活的大叔確實需要一定程度上的&ldquo;逃避現實&rdquo;，而看異世界穿越題材作品則是最為便利的方法&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"49b6d24d74704d8c14f2c3a48ba089c589a18945","tid":741977,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"近排淨係睇左RE:0,OVERLOAD,騎士&amp;魔法, <br />\n都唔算好熱衷異世界穿越作品啫<br />\n同埋覺得開唔開後宮都無所謂,唔開得照睇<br />\n<br />\n利申:魔法師"},{"pid":"56be4ff5336fbb89fa65a3de5ba0259c56e5dc51","tid":741977,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49b6d24d74704d8c14f2c3a48ba089c589a18945","tid":741977,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"近排淨係睇左RE:0,OVERLOAD,騎士&amp;魔法, <br />\n都唔算好熱衷異世界穿越作品啫<br />\n同埋覺得開唔開後宮都無所謂,唔開得照睇<br />\n<br />\n利申:魔法師"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:21:43.000Z","msg":"OVERLO<strong>R</strong>D先岩"},{"pid":"575e86f6b724aee447e44ad7db051d77dbd3f691","tid":741977,"uid":84128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:31:52.000Z","msg":"無職轉生ok<br />\n會反思返上一世有咩做唔好咁<br />\n睇改變<br />\n主角又唔係開哂外掛咁<br />\n其他就不了"},{"pid":"4f8a9ffa2aac89bc479e55e4156fbad59c13c42a","tid":741977,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:45:28.000Z","msg":"我睇廢萌黎逃避現實"},{"pid":"f76a3e7e18f94d4096adc337199ef02834560b99","tid":741977,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"Sorry囉<br />\n我係一個25歲既大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bced0a24cf6d4d8a48e49f4bf510604ddb983739","tid":741977,"uid":104432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f76a3e7e18f94d4096adc337199ef02834560b99","tid":741977,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"Sorry囉<br />\n我係一個25歲既大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime